OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy this
OL,6,Fevening with outbreaks of rain, mainly
OL,7,Facross Cumbria. Rain becoming more
OL,8,Fwidespread overnight and turning
OL,9,Fwintry over some of the hills in the
OL,10,Fnorth. Breezy along the coasts and
OL,11,Fhills.
OL,12,
OL,13,CFriday:FA damp start with outbreaks of
OL,14,Frain, perhaps hill snow too. Rain
OL,15,Fbecoming patchier through the
OL,16,Fafternoon but staying largely cloudy.
OL,17,FMuch cooler than Thursday, with a
OL,18,Fchilly night ahead.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
