OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FDry on
OL,6,FSaturday with some sunshine
OL,7,Fdeveloping. Often cloudier thereafter
OL,8,Fwith occasional patchy rain and
OL,9,Fdrizzle in places. Temperatures closer
OL,10,Fto average, with generally light winds.
